---
title: Pork al Mojo with Cuban Rice & Beans
description: Herbaceous, citrusy mojo sauce wakes up anything it touches, but juicy pork chops might be the ultimate pairing. Served on a bed of cilantro and lime-spiked beans and rice, this Cuban- inspired dish is guaranteed to wow.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-al-mojo-4709d09a.jpg
